A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-antics-could-harm-him-in-upcoming-criminal-trials-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709444104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e3f7a16080194819fbf962%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-antics-could-harm-him-in-upcoming-criminal-trials-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20will%20have%20to%20tone%20down%20the%20antics%20during%20his%20four%20criminal%20trials%2C%20attorneys%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hgetahun%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Getahun)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-antics-could-harm-him-in-upcoming-criminal-trials-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20India%20Needs%20To%20Do%20Urgently%20To%20Support%20Its%20Ageing%20Population%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03102110%2Fimage-1893.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoida%20(Uttar%20Pradesh)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20workforce%20will%20be%20middle-aged%3A%20The%20median%20age%20will%20increase%20to%2038%20in%202050%20from%2030%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iipsindia.ac.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FLASI_India_Report_2020_compressed.pdf%23page%3D49%5C%22%3Eprojections%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20by%20the%20longitudinal%20ageing%20study%20in%20india%20(LASI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapp.iussp.org%2Fsessions%2Fpapp101_s01%2FPAPP101_s01_090_010.html%5C%22%3E%20demographic%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E%20process%2C%20in%20which%20the%20number%20of%20births%20and%20deaths%20fall.%20When%20the%20birth%20rate%20remains%20constant%20as%20death%20rates%20of%20both%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%20decline%2C%20the%20population%20experiences%20a%20bulge%20(and%20an%20economic%20boom).%20However%2C%20if%20the%20birth%20rate%20falls%2C%20the%20number%20of%20working%20age%20people%20reduces%20and%20the%20proportion%20of%20the%20elderly%20increases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proportion%20of%20elderly%20is%20increasing%20in%20the%20less%20developed%20nations%2C%20with%20about%20eight%20in%2010%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20elderly%20people%20expected%20to%20be%20living%20in%20developing%20nations%20in%202050.%20This%20causes%20a%20change%20in%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC2781829%2F%5C%22%3E%20age-dependency%20ratio%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20consequences%20for%20the%20allocation%20of%20resources%20towards%20education%2C%20healthcare%20and%20social%20security%20for%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20we%20live%20longer%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20elderly%20are%20able%20to%20lead%20a%20healthy%2C%20fulfilling%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20this%20United%20Nations%20Population%20Fund%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.unfpa.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpub-pdf%2Fanalytical_paper_7_-_determinants_of_public_health_care_utilization_by_elderly_in_india_-_final.pdf%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Health%20and%20well-being%20are%20determined%20not%20only%20by%20our%20genes%20and%20personal%20characteristics%20but%20also%20by%20the%20physical%20and%20social%20environments%20in%20which%20we%20live%20our%20lives%2C%20said%20A.B.%20Dey%2C%20a%20geriatrics%20specialist%20and%20head%20of%20the%20geriatrics%20department%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aiims.edu%2Findex.php%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3EAll%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20principal%20investigators%20on%20the%20LASI%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEnvironments%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20determining%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20capacity%20across%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20life%20course%20and%20into%20older%20age%2C%20and%20also%20how%20well%20we%20adjust%20to%20loss%20of%20function%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20adversity%20that%20we%20may%20experience%20at%20different%20stages%20of%20life%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20in%20later%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20older%20people%20and%20the%20environments%20in%20which%20they%20live%20poised%20to%20change%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20government%20act%20now%20to%20allow%20healthy%20ageing%2C%20according%20to%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20part%20of%20our%20series%20on%20ageing%20India%20analyses%20the%20problems%20before%20the%20country%20as%20it%20advances%20in%20age%20without%20necessarily%20advancing%20economically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20demographic%20transition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%202050%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20children%20in%20the%20Indian%20population%20under%20the%20age%20of%2014%20will%20be%20less%20than%20that%20of%20the%20elderly%20(over%2060%20years)%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20India.%20While%20those%20over%20the%20age%20of%2060%20will%20be%2019.5%25%20of%20the%20population%20(nearly%20one%20in%20five)%2C%20those%20under%20the%20age%20of%2014%20will%20be%2018.5%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%22aede0dc3-47ff-49be-bda4-4e195eb868aa%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Age%20Structure%20Of%20The%20Indian%20Population%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20Kerala%20has%20the%20highest%20proportion%20of%20elderly%20population%20at%2019.6%25%20(which%20is%20almost%20equal%20to%20the%20projected%20proportion%20of%20elderly%20for%20India%20in%202050).%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Maharashtra%20also%20have%20a%20high%20number%20of%20people%20aged%2060%20and%20above%2C%20as%20per%20LASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-id%3D%5C%228e61fd4f-6b93-4d84-8dac-29c136790dc1%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22interactive%5C%22%20data-title%3D%5C%22Percentage%20Of%20Elderly%20(Aged%2060%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20Above)%2C%202017-18%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20women%20are%20present%20in%20that%20age%20group%20than%20men%3A%20the%20sex%20ratio%20for%2060%20years%20and%20above%20is%201%2C065%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males.%20It%20is%20more%20skewed%20in%20urban%20areas%20(1%2C084%20women%20per%201%2C000%20men)%20than%20in%20rural%20areas%20(1%2C055%20women%20per%201%2C000%20men).%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20sex%20ratio%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%20children%20is%20higher%20in%20rural%20(941)%20than%20in%20urban%20areas%20(912).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20because%20women%20live%20longer%20than%20men%2C%20as%20per%20economist%20Arun%20Kumar%2C%20a%20retired%20professor%20of%20economics%20from%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20bear%20children%2C%20so%20they%20have%20a%20stronger%20immune%20system.%20Secondly%2C%20women%20have%20largely%20been%20at%20home%2C%20which%20is%20a%20less%20stressful%20thing%20than%20going%20out%20to%20work%20or%20in%20earlier%20times%2C%20hunting.%20High%20stress%20levels%20lead%20to%20earlier%20deaths%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrban%20women%20have%20access%20to%20better%20healthcare%2C%20more%20nutrition%20and%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20poor%20than%20rural%20women%2C%20which%20explains%20why%20the%20sex%20ratio%20is%20higher%20for%20urban%20women%20in%20that%20age%20group%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoss%20of%20income%20for%20country%20and%20household%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20countries%20where%20the%20population%20is%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS2212828X14000371%3Fvia%3Dihub%5C%22%3Egrowing%20old%20before%20growing%20rich%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20meaning%20the%20growth%20in%20incomes%20for%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20population%20has%20not%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20at%20present%2062%20dependents%20(children%20under%20the%20age%20of%2014%20and%20old%20people%20above%20the%20age%20of%2065)%20for%20every%20100%20working%20people%20in%20India%2C%20as%20per%20the%20LASI%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iipsindia.ac.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FLASI_India_Report_2020_compressed.pdf%23page%3D96%5C%22%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20the%20population%20of%20the%20youth%20will%20continue%20to%20increase%20for%20the%20next%2015-20%20years%2C%20unless%20they%20have%20jobs%2C%20the%20dependency%20ratio%20will%20remain%20high%20and%20the%20demographic%20dividend%20will%20become%20a%20demographic%20disaster%2C%20said%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAutomation%20also%20threatens%20to%20replace%20workers%20in%20call%20centres%2C%20back%20process%20jobs%2C%20etc.%2C%20which%20will%20hurt%20employment%20prospects%20further%2C%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20address%20the%20problems%20of%20health%2C%20education%20and%20employment%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iipsindia.ac.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F62_Insights_into_labor_force.pdf%5C%22%3E%2036%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20elderly%20(aged%2060%20years%20and%20older)%20are%20currently%20working.%20Of%20these%2C%20about%20a%20fifth%20(21%25)%20are%20agricultural%20labourers%2C%20meaning%20they%20have%20no%20employer-provided%20social%20security%20or%20pensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPensions%20and%20family%20support%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsph.harvard.edu%2Fpgda%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F1288%2F2018%2F03%2FPGDA_WP_148_Economic-Perspectives-on-Global-Population-Aging_Demography-is-Not-Destiny.pdf%5C%22%3E%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20elderly%2C%20chief%20among%20which%20is%20healthcare.%20Only%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iipsindia.ac.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FLASI_India_Report_2020_compressed.pdf%5C%22%3E%205.7%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20elderly%20get%20pensions%2C%20as%20per%20the%20LASI%20study.%20In%20addition%2C%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.unfpa.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpub-pdf%2FThematicPaper2-Womenandageing.pdf%5C%22%3E59%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20older%20women%20do%20not%20receive%20any%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%2C%20safety%20and%20dignity%3A%20What%20the%20state%20has%20to%20secure%20for%20the%20elderly%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20shortage%20in%20the%20labour%20force%20and%20reduced%20savings%2C%20population%20ageing%20presents%20a%20new%20set%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsph.harvard.edu%2Fpgda%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F1288%2F2018%2F03%2FPGDA_WP_148_Economic-Perspectives-on-Global-Population-Aging_Demography-is-Not-Destiny.pdf%5C%22%3E%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20This%20may%20require%20realigning%20primary%20healthcare%20services%20to%20better%20care%20for%20the%20new%20diseases%20among%20the%20target%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leading%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.who.int%2Fcountries%2F356%5C%22%3E%20cause%20of%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20are%20non-communicable%20diseases%20%E2%80%93%20heart%20disease%2C%20cancer%2C%20chronic%20respiratory%20diseases%2C%20diabetes%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%93%20for%20both%20men%20and%20women.%20Developed%20states%20such%20as%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20a%20higher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphfi.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F2017-India-State-Level-Disease-Burden-Initiative-Full-Report.pdf%23page%3D21%5C%22%3Eburden%20of%20NCDs%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20etc.%2C%20according%20to%20national%20health%20data%20analysed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%2C%20Public%20Health%20Foundation%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Institute%20for%20Health%20Metrics%20and%20Evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttention%20is%20required%20for%20age-related%20diseases%20such%20as%20those%20caused%20by%20an%20inevitable%20biological%20decline%20(cataract%20and%20macular%20degeneration%20that%20affect%20eyesight%2C%20sensorineural%20deafness%2C%20osteoporosis%20and%20osteoarthritis%20which%20weaken%20the%20bones%2C%20cognitive%20impairments%20like%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20disease%20and%20dementia%2C%20heart%20failure%2C%20etc.)%2C%20metabolic%20diseases%20(hypertension%2C%20coronary%20artery%20disease%2C%20stroke%2C%20diabetes)%2C%20or%20environmental%20exposure%20(cancer%2C%20COPD%2C%20etc.)%2C%20according%20to%20Dey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlder%20people%20commonly%20present%20to%20the%20health%20system%20with%20cognitive%20decline%2C%20frail%20health%2C%20increased%20risk%20of%20infection%2C%20heart%20attack%2C%20stroke%2C%20cancer%2C%20visual%20impairment%2C%20deafness%2C%20depression%20etc.%2C%20in%20multiple%20numbers%20and%20combinations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment-funded%20health%20insurance%20is%20available%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2FPM-JAY%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20bottom%2040%25%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20Union%20government%20provides%20assistive%20devices%20to%20the%20elderly%20from%20the%20below-poverty-line%20category%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-india-gov-in.translate.goog%2Fspotlight%2Frashtriya-vayoshri-yojana%3F_x_tr_sl%3Den%26_x_tr_tl%3Dhi%26_x_tr_hl%3Dhi%26_x_tr_pto%3Dtc%5C%22%3ERashtriya%20Vayoshri%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%201999%2C%20after%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20National%20Policy%20on%20Older%20Persons%20and%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20National%20Programme%20for%20Health%20Care%20of%20Elderly%20in%202010%2C%20initiation%20of%20the%20Integrated%20Programme%20for%20Older%20Persons%20in%202018%2C%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20and%20Health%20and%20Wellness%20Centers%20etc.%20were%20steps%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20in%20securing%20the%20welfare%20of%20older%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fwhat-india-needs-to-do-urgently-to-support-its-ageing-population-897338%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2F%5C%22%3EIndiaSpend.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709443822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03102110%2Fimage-1893.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fwhat-india-needs-to-do-urgently-to-support-its-ageing-population%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%2020%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20will%20be%20over%2060%20years%20old%20in%202050.%20With%20family%20structures%20changing%20and%20existing%20state-provided%20services%20being%20inadequate%2C%20today%E2%80%99s%20working%20Indians%20need%20protection%20against%20loss%20of%20income%20and%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fwhat-india-needs-to-do-urgently-to-support-its-ageing-population%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Dhoni%2C%20Bravo%20groove%20in%20style%20playing%20dandiya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709443574000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108175108%2Cimgsize-33020.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Foff-the-field%2Findo-caribbean-dandiya-ms-dhoni-dwayne-bravo-groove-in-style-at-anant-ambanis-pre-wedding-festivities%2Farticleshow%2F108175044.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Clad%20in%20traditional%20Indian%20attire%2C%20Dhoni%20and%20Bravo%2C%20former%20teammates%20for%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Ki