of%20Vidisha%2C%20we%20are%20like%20family.%20The%20roadmap%20for%20Vidisha%20is%20ready.%20The%20BJP%20will%20win%20all%2029%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20state%20will%20put%2029%20garlands%20on%20PM%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVidisha%20is%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20BJP's%20fortresses%20in%20the%20country%20and%20was%20won%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20in%201991%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20in%202009%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20and%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20has%20been%20named%20the%20candidate%20from%20Guna%2C%20a%20seat%20he%20had%20held%20since%202002%20until%20his%20loss%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Krishna%20Pal%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoyalists%20Rewarded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20four%20of%20Mr%20Chouhan's%20loyalists%20have%20got%20tickets.%20Former%20Bhopal%20mayor%20Alok%20Sharma%20(who%20lost%20from%20the%20Bhopal%20Uttar%20seat%20in%20last%20year's%20Assembly%20elections)%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Bhopal%2C%20state%20Kisan%20Morcha%20head%20Darshan%20Singh%20Chaudhary%20from%20Hoshangabad%20and%20sitting%20MP%20Rodmal%20Nagar%20from%20Rajgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnita%20Nagar%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20is%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20former%20chief%20minister's%20loyalist%2C%20Nagar%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20has%20been%20named%20the%20candidate%20for%20the%20Ratlam-Jhabua%20(ST)%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20Singh%20Kushwah%2C%20a%20loyalist%20of%20Assembly%20Speaker%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20has%20been%20given%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20Gwalior%20seat%20despite%20losing%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20from%20the%20Gwalior%20Rural%20constituency%20last%20year.%20Two%20other%20loyalists%20of%20Mr%20Tomar%2C%20sitting%20MP%20Sandhya%20Rai%20and%20former%20MLA%20Shivmangal%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%