%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20planted%20at%20the%20Kadri%20Manjunatha%20temple.%20Investigators%20had%20found%20that%20the%20Mangaluru%20cooker%20blast%20was%20%26quot%3BIslamic%20State-sponsored%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20operative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%20investigators%20have%20gathered%20certain%20information%20from%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20footage%20from%20the%20city's%20public%20transport%20buses%20was%20also%20being%20analysed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20probe%20to%20nab%20the%20culprit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20teams%20have%20been%20formed%20to%20investigate.%20In-depth%20investigation%20is%20going%20on%20with%20seriousness%2C%20some%20traces%20have%20been%20found.%20Some%20information%20has%20been%20gathered%20from%20CCTV%20footage...there%20is%20information%20that%20he%20(suspect)%20had%20come%20by%20bus.%20So%2C%2026%20buses%20have%20been%20verified%20at%20Bangalore%20Metropolitan%20Transport%20Corporation%20(BMTC)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Parameshwara%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Btheory%20of%20elimination%26quot%3B%2C%20more%20buses%20are%20being%20verified%20for%20footage%2C%20as%20BMTC%20buses%20have%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20moment%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20say%20whether%20any%20organisation%20or%20an%20individual%20was%20involved%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20said.%20There%20were%20certain%20theories%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20cafe%20last%20night%2C%20expressing%20suspicion%20that%20someone%20might%20have%20done%20it%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Bheartburn%26quot%3B%2C%20unable%20to%20digest%20the%20cafe's%20success%20and%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20look%20into%20all%20angles.%20Whichever%20angle%20it%20might%20be%2C%20we%20will%20verify%20them%20and%20catch%20the%20culprits%20behind%20the%20blast%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20sources%2C%20images%20of%20the%20suspect's%20movement%20have%20been%20captured%20by%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20at%20Rameshwaram%20cafe%20and%20those%20nearby.%20The%20CCTV%20footage%20shows%20the%20suspect%20with%20a%20bag%2C%20wearing%20a%20cap%20and%20mask%2C%20walking%20and%20looking%20at%20wristwatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20positive%20about%20the%20leads%20we%20are%20getting%20in%20nabbing%20the%20culprit%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESleuths%20from%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20and%20the%20National%20Security%20Guard%20(NSG)%20reached%20the%20spot%20to%20help%20the%20local%20police%20in%20the%20investigation%20and%20shared%20some%20inputs%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709440860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F4m2tq1cg_siddaramaiah-_625x300_03_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-blast-siddaramaiah-visits-bengaluru-cafe-blast-site-cops-intensify-probe-5166605%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20police%20intensified%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20March%201%20bomb%20blast%20at%20a%20city%20eatery%20that%20left%2010%20injured%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20on%20Saturday%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20those%20behind%20the%20incident%20will%20be%20nabbed%20at%20the%20earliest%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-blast-siddaramaiah-visits-bengaluru-cafe-blast-site-cops-intensify-probe-5166605%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Frameshwaram-cafe-blast-siddaramaiah-visits-bengaluru-cafe-blast-site-cops-intensify-probe-5166605%2Famp