f%20contagion%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4-1024x726.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4-1024x726.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4-300x213.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093218%2Fthe-moral-contagion_4.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-699832%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22596%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20illustration%20from%20%E2%80%98The%20Moral%20Contagion%E2%80%99%20by%20Julia%20Hauser%20and%20Sarnath%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%20also%20presents%20the%20history%20of%20science%20with%20a%20firm%20eye%20on%20the%20role%20of%20colonial%20practices%20%E2%80%93%20placing%20laconic%20credit%20for%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20disease%20to%20the%20British%20and%20their%20commerce%20wherever%20due.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBanerjee%E2%80%99s%20art%20is%20the%20jester%20traipsing%20through%20the%20expanse%20of%20the%20book.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20pages%20have%20illustrations%20%E2%80%93%20so%20the%20total%20number%20of%20drawings%20is%20close%20to%20130.%20The%20text%20%E2%80%93%20never%20dry%20but%20certainly%20more%20serious%20than%20the%20art%20%E2%80%93%20scooches%20to%20a%20corner%20to%20make%20way%20for%20it.%20Banerjee%20harnesses%20his%20telltale%20style%20%E2%80%93%20crayon%20marks%20visible%2C%20faces%20dour%20and%20experiences%20muted%20on%20one%20page%20and%20viscerally%20exaggerated%20on%20the%20next.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20sick%20man%20in%20Bombay%20stretches%20comically%20as%20two%20policemen%20drag%20him%20away%20by%20the%20legs%2C%20almost%20bored.%20Things%20happen%20to%20people%20he%20draws%2C%20but%20not%20acutely%20enough%20to%20rob%20his%20characters%20of%20humour.%20It%20is%20minimal%2C%20so%20whenever%20it%20is%20opulent%2C%20the%20details%20take%20you%20by%20surprise.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPages%2082%20and%2083%20are%20something%20of%20a%20triumph.%20Here%2C%20a%20body%20is%20seen%20lurching%20into%20the%20sea%20from%20a%20ship%20instituted%20as%20a%20plague%20hospital%20off%20Hong%20Kong%20by%20the%20British.%20The%20night%20is%20dark%20and%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20ship%20is%20perhaps%20a%20testament%20to%20how%20stuffy%2C%20how%20claustrophobic%20such%20an%20exercise%20must%20have%20felt%20to%20Chinese%20colonial%20subjects%20suffering%20from%20an%20exhausting%20disease.%20The%20drawing%20occupies%20almost%20one-and-a-half%20pages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20ubiquitousness%20of%20injustice%2C%20some%20details%20are%20particularly%20sobering.%20Like%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20plague%20came%20back%20to%20Hong%20Kong%20every%20year%20for%20three%20decades%20in%20the%20late%2019th%20and%20early%2020th%20centuries%2C%20and%20yet%20there%20was%20no%20interest%20in%20investing%20in%20the%20health%20of%20the%20workers%20who%20ran%20it.%20While%20those%20suffering%20from%20long%20COVID%20continue%20to%20remind%20us%20of%20the%20crushing%20after-effects%20of%20it%2C%20while%20those%20who%20lost%20loved%20ones%20in%20disease%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcoronavirus-national-lockdown-migrant-workers-dead%5C%22%3Ealso%20thanks%20to%20harebrained%20policy%20decisions%20surrounding%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20unlikely%20to%20ever%20forget%20it%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20exaggeration%20to%20say%20that%20the%20pandemic%20lies%20forgotten%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20Conclusion%2C%20Hauser%20says%20that%20even%20this%20is%20common.%20Even%20more%20chastening%2C%20often%20it%20is%20%E2%80%98bigger%E2%80%99%20political%20concerns%20%E2%80%93%20like%20that%20forever%20friend%20to%20civilisation%2C%20war%20%E2%80%93%20that%20necessitates%20the%20%E2%80%98end%E2%80%99%20of%20disease.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709439401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F03093231%2Fthe-moral-contagion_1-e1709438696342.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-covid-moral-contagion-julia-hauser-sarnath-banerjee%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20many%20reasons%20why%20'The%20Moral%20Contagion'%20by%20Julia%20Hauser%20and%20Sarnath%20Banerjee%20acts%20as%20succour%20and%20makes%20our%20current%20age%20feel%20less%20wretched.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-covid-moral-contagion-julia-hauser-sarnath-banerjee%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20PM%20Modi%20to%20chair%20Council%20of%20Ministers'%20meet%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709439209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F23%2Ffull%2F1708674205-9258.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-lok-sabha-polls-pm-modi-to-chair-council-of-ministers-meet-today-124030300065_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20is%20likely%20to%20announce%20the%20poll%20schedule%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-lok-sabha-polls-pm-modi-to-chair