0see%20my%20son%20so%20scared%20and%20thought%20to%20calm%20him%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7169204217310502912%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222093%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dialled%20the%20security%20helpline%20on%20Ola%20and%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20police.%20The%20father-son%20duo%20stood%20outside%20the%20car%20and%20the%20driver%20refused%20to%20return%20Mr%20Verma's%20bag.%20When%20he%20confronted%20him%20and%20clicked%20his%20picture%2C%20the%20driver%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20car%20and%20slapped%20him.%20%26quot%3BI%20dialed%20security%20helpline%20from%20the%20%23OlaApp%20instantly%20and%20called%20Police%20Helpline.Me%20and%20my%20son%20was%20standing%20outside%2C%20and%20this%20guy%20took%20my%20bag.%20Meanwhile%20when%20I%20refused%20to%20pay%20him%20and%20click%20his%20picture%20with%20my%20bag.%20He%20came%20out%20and%20slapped%20me.%20There%20was%20a%20gentleman%20going%20(another%20cab%20driver)%20he%20came%20and%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20user%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLater%20I%20took%20my%20son%20to%20a%20bench%20on%20footpath%20and%20was%20still%20on%20call%20with%20the%20helpline%20guy%20of%20ANI%20Technologies%20PVT%20LTD.%20The%20guy%20over%20phone%20suggested%20me%20not%20to%20pay%20or%20talk%20to%20the%20driver%20and%20that's%20what%20I%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Verma%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20triggered%20the%20driver%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20phone%20was%20on%20loudspeaker%20and%20the%20driver%20slapped%20him%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%20the%20another%20driver%20stopped%20him.%20The%20driver%20took%20two%20goons%20along%20with%20him%20(maybe%20they%20had%20some%20plans%20to%20loot)%20but%20since%20there%20were%203-4%20people%20by%20that%20time.%20All%20three%20ran%20(other%20two%20were%20on%20bike).%20I%20called%20%23UPPolice%20and%20they%20came%20on%20the%20spot.%20But%20that%20was%20of%20no%20use.%20The%20driver%20who%20saved%20me%20took%20me%20to%20the%20airport%20and%20told%20me%20that%20no%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20on%20driver.%20Whereas%20Uber%20suspends%20such%20drivers%20and%20blacklists%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20said%20that%20the%20company%20had%20not%20yet%20called%20him%20and%20closed%20the%20complaint%20ticket%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20incident.%20He%20said%20that%20his%20son%20was%20distressed%20by%20the%20entire%20situation.%20He%20wrote%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20thinking%20to%20even%20expect%20a%20call%20from%20Ola%20but%20till%20date%20not%20even%20a%20single%20call%20from%20their%20side.%20SHOCKINGLY%20the%20complaint%20was%20closed%20by%20Ola%20company%20in%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20and%20till%20date%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken.%20My%20son%20was%20so%20shocked%20that%20night%20that%20he%20cried%20out%20loud%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20reached%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20also%20shared%20the%20details%20of%20the%20cab%20and%20complaint%20ticket%20number%20and%20urged%20internet%20users%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20ride-hailing%20service%20and%20consider%20other%20alternatives.%20He%20concluded%20the%20post%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%20such%20driver%20should%20be%20allowed%20on%20road.%20People%20should%20STOP%20using%20Ola%20and%20use%20%23Uber%20instead%20it%20might%20cost%20you%20more%20in%20terms%20of%20money%20but%20cheaper%20in%20terms%20of%20your%20safety%20and%20dignity.%20Bhavish%20Aggarwal%20should%20be%20held%20responsible%20in%20this%20case%20directly%20for%20creating%20such%20culture.%20It%20is%20my%20honest%20effort%20to%20protect%20atleast%20a%20few%2C%20who%20expect%20to%20use%20Ola%20as%20a%20safe%20car%20service.%20Again%20%23StopUsingOla%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20has%20amassed%20a%20lot%20of%20reactions%20from%20social%20media%20users%20who%20have%20expressed%20support%20for%20the%20user%20and%20called%20on%20Ola%20to%20take%20action.%20This%20distressing%20episode%20has%20rekindled%20concerns%20about%20ride-hailing%20companies'%20responsibility%20and%20passenger%20safety%2C%20leading%20to%20requests%20for%20extensive%20reforms%20and%20awareness.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20absolutely%20horrific!%20I'm%20so%20sorry%20you%20had%20to%20go%20through%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20remember%20when%20I%20had%20an%20issue%20with%20an%20Ola%20driver%20a%20few%20years%20back%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20Ola%20call%20centre%20people%20were%20keen%20on%20was%20on%20to%20stop%20me%20from%20registering%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20the%20driver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BTime%20to%20shift%20on%20Uber%20or%20Rapido%20from%20Ola..!%20I%20never%20use%20Ola%20for%20such%20thing..!%20Bhavish%20Aggarwal%20has%20shifted%20his%20focus%20from%20Ola%20to%20building%20other%20startup.%20And%20now%20seems%20like%20no%20one%20cares%20about%20customer%20experience%20in%20Ola.%20%23StopUsingOla%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20file%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20and%20negligence%20of%20service%20against%20all%20responsible.%20Start%20with%20consumer%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCould%20not%20agree%20more%2C%20I%20have%20had%20my%20worst%20experiences%20with%20Ola%20Cabs.%20The%20drivers%20cancel%20cabs%20last%20minute%20and%20ask%20for%20cash.%20They%20stop%20the%20cab%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20quiet%20road%20to%20have%20%26quot%3BPan%20masala%26quot%3B.%20The%20cars%20are%20mostly%20very%20dirty%20.%20The%20cab%20guys%20play%20real%20crap%20songs%20on%20a%20very%20high%20volume.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Ola%20drivers%20don't%20put%20on%20the%20AC's%20sighting%20random%20reasons%20and%20to%20make%20things%20even%20worse%20..the%20customer%20service%20won't%20respond.%20Worst%20company%20to%20travel%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BFile%20a%20case%20with%20the%20consumer%20forum%20and%20also%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20the%20said%20driver%20and%20the%20company%20and%20claim%20damages%2Fcompensation%20from%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOla%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709438340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fa6sirnn8_driver_625x300_03_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasked-me-to-pay-extra-man-assaulted-by-ola-driver-in-front-of-son-demands-action-5166531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Verma%20said%20that%20the%20company%20had%20not%20yet%20called%20him%20and%20closed%20the%20complaint%20ticket%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20after%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasked-me-to-pay-extra-man-assaulted-by-ola-driver-in-front-of-son-demands-action-5166531%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasked-me-to-pay-extra-man-assaulted-by-ola-driver-in-front-of-son-demands-action-5166531%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fasked-me-to-pay-extra-man-assaulted-by-ola-driver-in-front-of-son-demands-action-5166531%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDon't%20Need%26quot%3B%3A%20Gavaskar%20To%20%26quot%3BNames%20Who%20Think%20India%20Can't%20Win%20Without%20Them%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20vs%20England%20series%20was%20in%20many%20ways%20an%20acid%20Test%20for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.n