lded%20them%2C%20and%20encouraged%20them%20to%20play%20their%20natural%20game.%20This%20shows%20that%20whether%20we%20have%20big%20names%20or%20not%2C%20if%20we%20have%20players%20with%20big%20hearts%20then%20we%20can%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20youngsters%20like%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Akash%20Deep%2C%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20have%20so%20far%20starred%20in%20the%20series%2C%20former%20Australia%20captain%20Ian%20Chappel%20made%20sure%20that%20the%20leadership%20skills%20of%20Rohit%20is%20also%20among%20the%20most%20talked%20topics.%20Chappel%20feels%20that%20Rohit's%20ability%20as%20a%20leader%20is%20%26quot%3Boften%20overlooked%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20sudden%20shuffling%20of%20the%20Indian%20side%20after%20a%20prolonged%20period%20of%20selection%20stability%2C%20the%20leadership%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20often%20overlooked.%20Rohit%2C%20in%20his%20quiet%20but%20efficient%20way%2C%20is%20a%20very%20different%20leader%20from%20the%20aggressive%20and%20highly%20visible%20Ben%20Stokes.%20His%20capable%20handling%20of%20the%20many%20changes%20to%20personnel%20and%20the%20tough%20loss%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20shows%20his%20resilience.%20He%20also%20produced%20a%20masterful%20century%20when%20the%20Indian%20team%20needed%20it%2C%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20third%20Test%2C%20to%20confirm%20he%20wasn't%20a%20ceremonial%20captain%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Chappell%20on%20ESPNcricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709438340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F5kgot2c8_india-test_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fdont-need-sunil-gavaskars-stern-message-to-big-names-who-think-india-cant-win-without-them-5163896%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20vs%20England%3A%20India%20gave%20debut%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20Dhruv%20Jurel%2C%20Akash%20Deep%2C%20Rajat%20Patidar%20and%20yet%20se