%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20begins%20with%20a%20small%20Florida%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Camshaft%20Capital%20Fund%2C%20accused%20of%20assisting%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20in%20concealing%20%24533%20million.%20This%20staggering%20amount%2C%20crucial%20to%20the%20ongoing%20financial%20tussle%2C%20was%20initially%20held%20by%20Byju's%20Alpha%20Inc.%2C%20a%20bankrupt%20shell%20company%20affiliated%20with%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn.%20Lenders%2C%20owed%20%241.2%20billion%2C%20took%20control%20of%20Byju's%20Alpha%20after%20it%20defaulted%20on%20its%20loan.%20The%20%24533%20million%2C%20allegedly%20transferred%20to%20Camshaft%20Capital%20Fund%2C%20was%20subsequently%20moved%20to%20an%20undisclosed%20offshore%20trust%20by%20Raveendran's%20brother%2C%20Riju%20Ravindran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Alpha%20had%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20protection%20over%20the%20%241.2%20billion%20loan%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lenders%2C%20seeking%20repayment%20of%20the%20%241.2%20billion%20and%20the%20elusive%20%24533%20million%2C%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20legal%20struggle%20with%20Byju's.%20A%20court%20ruling%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Delaware%20gave%20lenders%20control%20of%20Alpha%2C%20a%20decision%20now%20under%20appeal%20by%20Riju%20Ravindran.%20A%20US%20court%20on%20Friday%20dismissed%20Camshaft%20Capital%20Fund's%20attempt%20to%20avoid%20disclosing%20details%20about%20the%20cash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20lawyer%2C%20Benjamin%20Finestone%2C%20revealed%20during%20the%20hearing%20that%20the%20%24533%20million%20was%20initially%20transferred%20to%20Camshaft%20Capital%20Fund%20before%20being%20moved%20to%20an%20unnamed%20offshore%20trust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPotential%20Sanctions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECamshaft%20Capital%20Fund%20has%20resisted%20disclosing%20information%20about%20the%20money%2C%20citing%20its%20%26quot%3Bduty%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20clients%20and%20redirecting%20inquiries%20to%20a%20Delaware%20company%20called%20Inspilearn%2C%20a%20Delaware%20company%20that%20allegedly%20received%20the%20money%20from%20Camshaft%20before%20its%20transfer%20to%20the%20unnamed%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20US%20judge%20labelled%20Camshaft's%20reluctance%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20red%20flag.%26quot%3B%20Failure%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20court's%20order%20could%20lead%20to%20sanctions%2C%20as%20the%20judge%20threatened%20a%20%26quot%3Bshow%20cause%26quot%3B%20hearing%20on%20Monday%20if%20the%20information%20is%20not%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeries%20Of%20Setbacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%2C%20once%20valued%20at%20%2422%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20has%20faced%20a%20tumultuous%20period%20since%20early%202023.%20Auditor%20resignations%2C%20lenders%20initiating%20bankruptcy%20proceedings%2C%20and%20a%20US%20lawsuit%20challenging%20loan%20terms%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20company's%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20is%20also%20grappling%20with%20financial%20challenges%20that%20extend%20beyond%20courtrooms.%20Mr%20Raveendran%20informed%20employees%20recently%20that%20the%20company%20is%20unable%20to%20process%20salaries%20due%20to%20a%20legal%20dispute%20with%20investors%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20Reuters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju's%20started%20its%20venture%20in%202006%20by%20offering%20classes%20for%20MBA%20aspirants%20preparing%20for%20the%20CAT%20exam.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20edtech%20firm%20diversified%20its%20offerings%2C%20extending%20its%20reach%20from%20postgraduate%20to%20undergraduate%20and%20eventually%20school%20students.%20In%202015%2C%20it%20launched%20Byju's%20learning%20app%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20company%20to%20become%20India's%20first%20ed-tech%20unicorn%20in%20just%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709434560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fmh11kjs8_byju-raveendran-afp-650_625x300_01_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22or