-with-gaza-peace-deal-as-us-airdrops-begin%2Famp_articleshow%2F108171287.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Christian%20pop-up%20nightclub%20in%20Nashville%20plays%20Jesus%20rap%20and%20forbids%20twerking%2C%20drinking%2C%20and%20smoking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Attendees%20at%20The%20Cove%2C%20an%2018-and-up%2C%20pop-up%20Christian%20nightclub%2C%20dance%20in%20unison%20on%20February%2017%2C%202024%2C%20in%20Nashville%2C%20Tennessee.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e3a8cb90413ab8e1d8a4c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAttendees%20at%20The%20Cove%2C%20an%2018-and-up%2C%20pop-up%20Christian%20nightclub%2C%20dance%20in%20unison%20on%20February%2017%2C%202024%2C%20in%20Nashville%2C%20Tennessee.%3Cp%3EJessie%20Wardarski%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20pop-up%20Christian%20nightclub%20is%20gaining%20traction%20among%20a%20young%2C%20diverse%20crowd%20looking%20for%20community.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20club%2C%20which%20plays%20religious%20rap%20and%20hip-hop%2C%20wants%20to%20counter%20the%20corny%20Christian%20stereotype.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20have%20rules%20though%3A%20attendees%20must%20be%2018%20and%20cannot%20twerk%2C%20drink%2C%20or%20smoke.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20crowd%20at%20a%20Nashville%20nightclub%20was%20ready%20to%20dance%20under%20the%20strobe%20lights%20to%20a%20throbbing%20mix%20of%20hip-hop%2C%20rap%20and%20Latin%20beats.%20But%20first%20they%20gathered%20to%20pray%20and%20praise%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20were%20announced%20on%20the%20dance%20floor%20by%20a%20mic-carrying%20emcee%20to%20more%20than%20200%20clubgoers%20blanketed%20by%20thick%20smoke%20machine%20fog%3A%20%26quot%3BRule%20No.%201%3A%20No%20twerking.%20Second%20rule%3A%20No%20drinking.%20And%20a%20third%20rule%3A%20No%20smoking.%26quot%3B%20The%20last%20unspoken%20rule%20seemed%20obvious%20by%20then%3A%20No%20secular%20music%20%E2%80%94%20the%20playlist%20would%20be%20all%20Christian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthecovenash%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Cove%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pop-up%2C%2018-and-up%20Christian%20nightclub%20was%20launched%20last%20year%20by%20seven%20Black%20Christian%20men%20in%20their%2020s%20%E2%80%94%20among%20them%20an%20Ivy%20League-educated%20financial%20analyst%2C%20musicians%20and%20social%20media%20experts%20%E2%80%94%20who%20sought%20to%20build%20a%20thriving%20community%20and%20a%20welcoming%20space%20for%20young%20Christians%20outside%20houses%20of%20worship.%20The%20launch%20comes%20at%20a%20post-pandemic%20time%20of%20dwindling%20church%20attendance%2C%20especially%20among%20Black%20Protestants%20that%20surveys%20say%20is%20unmatched%20by%20any%20other%20major%20religious%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20ourselves%20experienced%20a%20pain%20point%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20find%20community%20outside%20of%20our%20church%2C%20not%20knowing%20what%20to%20do%20to%20have%20fun%20without%20feeling%20bad%20for%20doing%20stuff%20that's%20conflicting%20to%20our%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eric%20Diggs%2C%20The%20Cove's%2024-year-old%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20wasn't%20a%20space%20to%20cultivate%20that.%20So%2C%20we%20created%20it%20ourselves%20out%20of%20that%20pain%20point%20%E2%80%94%20the%20loneliness%2C%20the%20anxiety%2C%20depression%2C%20COVID%2C%20and%20the%20long%20quarantine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProving%20that%20Christians%20can%20be%20cool%20%E2%80%93%20not%20corny%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20their%20first%20monthly%20party%20in%20November%2C%20they%20set%20an%20ambitious%20goal%3A%20get%201%2C000%20followers%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BWe%20ended%20up%20getting%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20followers%20before%20our%20first%20event%2C%20which%20was%20insane%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eric's%20brother%2C%20Jordan%20Diggs%2C%2022%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20club's%20social%20media%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChristians%20get%20a%20rep%20for%20being%20corny.%20And%20we%20want%20to%20show%20that%20Christians%20can%20be%20normal%2C%20can%20be%20cool.%20And%20they%20can%20have%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20equally%20popular%20event%20was%20timed%20to%20ring%20in%20the%20New%20Year.%20A%20third%20was%20held%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20weeks%2C%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fthecovenash%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20under%20hashtags%20like%20%23jesuschrist%20%23nightclubs%20%E2%80%94%20club%20organizers%20asked%20people%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20dance%20the%20worship%20night%20away%20and%20look%20their%20best%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20pull%20up%2C%20we%20expect%20to%20see%20you%20in%20your%20Holiest%20Drip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20mid-February%20event%2C%20many%20in%20the%20racially%20and%20ethnically%20diverse%20crowd%20wore%20a%20rainbow%20of%20vivid%20colors%20%E2%80%94%20fluorescent%20turquoise%2C%20electric%20orange%2C%20neon%20pink%20%E2%80%94%20in%20their%20Nike%2C%20Adidas%20and%20New%20Balance%20sneakers.%20Or%20hoodies%20with%20images%20of%20Jesus%20and%20varsity%20jackets%20with%20Scripture%20from%20the%20Bible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jade%20Russell%20of%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20dances%20at%20The%20Cove.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e3a92d90413ab8e1d8a4d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222543%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJade%20Russell%20of%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20dances%20at%20The%20Cove.%3Cp%3EJessie%20Wardarski%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20surprised%20me%20the%20most%20is%20the%20diversity%2C%20honestly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aaron%20Dews%2C%20one%20of%20the%20club%20founders.%20%26quot%3BWith%20us%20being%20seven%20Black%20guys%2C%20just%20seeing%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20type%20of%20people%20that%20we%20can%20bring%20in%2C%20and%20the%20unification%20around%20one%20idea%20has%20been%20incredibly%20encouraging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20trucks%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20awaited%20hungry%20clubbers.%20Inside%2C%20Benji%20Shuler%20sold%20vintage%20clothes%20with%20religious%20messages%20that%20hung%20from%20racks.%20A%20white%20T-shirt%20with%20the%20iconic%20Pepsi%20logo%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BJesus%3A%20The%20Choice%20of%20a%20New%20Generation%2C%26quot%3B%20echoing%20the%20soda%20company's%20tagline%20from%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20lieu%20of%20alcohol%2C%20vendors%20sold%20sports%20drinks%2C%20bottled%20water%20and%20soda.%20Organizers%20cheerfully%20set%20up%20early.%20They%20hung%20Christmas-style%20lights%20from%20ceilings%2C%20sang%20a%20cappella%20and%20rehearsed%20their%20best%20choreographed%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EClub%20becomes%20a%20destination%20for%20Christians%20near%20and%20far%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20impressed%20everyone%20with%20his%20dance%20moves%2C%20Garrett%20Bland%2C%2020%2C%20listened%20on%20his%20phone%20to%20%26quot%3BDeliver%20Me%2C%26quot%3B%20by%20gospel%20singer%20Donald%20Lawrence.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20letting%20the%20Lord%20into%20your%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20wearing%20a%20gold%20medallion%20around%20his%20neck%20inscribed%20with%20the%20Lord's%20Prayer%20and%20a%20beige%20hoodie%20that%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BGod%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20admired%20what%20The%20Cove's%20founders%20are%20trying%20to%20do%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20want%20to%20create%20a%20space%20for%20believers%20who%20want%20to%20come%20to%20the%20faith%20and%20have%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20blue%20hoodie%20embr