%22%3Efaith-and-culture%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20co-hosted%20by%20Darin%20Starks%2C%20one%20of%20the%20club's%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thought%2C%20this%20is%20cool%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20God%20glorifying%2C%26quot%3B%20Haynza%20Posala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20surreal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kim%20Posala%2C%20looking%20around%20as%20people%20in%20trucker%20hats%2C%20berets%20and%20baseball%20caps%20streamed%20into%20the%20club%20and%20were%20handed%20bracelets%20of%20different%20colors.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20community%20and%20that's%20what%20church%20is%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20The%20Cove's%20seven%20co-founders%2C%20Aaron%20Dews%2C%20raises%20his%20arms%20in%20worship%20after%20a%20night%20of%20dancing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e3a9a5ce7f1785b2e5ba35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20The%20Cove's%20seven%20co-founders%2C%20Aaron%20Dews%2C%20raises%20his%20arms%20in%20worship%20after%20a%20night%20of%20dancing.%3Cp%3EJessie%20Wardarski%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMic%20in%20hand%2C%20Carlton%20Batts%20Jr.%2C%20a%20musician%20who%20is%20one%20of%20the%20founders%20and%20who%20was%20the%20designated%20DJ%20and%20emcee%2C%20asked%20people%20on%20the%20dance%20floor%20questions%2C%20dividing%20them%20into%20groups%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20like%20prefer%20listening%20to%20music%2C%20come%20over%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20pointing%20to%20one%20side.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20prefer%20podcasts%2C%20over%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20church%20people%20can%20be%20really%20cliquey%2C%26quot%3B%20Batts%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20here%2C%20we%20give%20them%20prompts%2C%20so%20when%20we%20start%20the%20DJ%20set%20people%20are%20really%20comfortable%20dancing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20went%20wild%20when%20the%20DJ%20played%20%26qu