at%20it%20prolongs%20the%20agony%20of%20litigants%20and%20perpetuates%20the%20cycle%20of%20backlog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20major%20issues%20is%20that%20of%20%26quot%3Badjournment%20culture.%26quot%3B%20This%20practice%2C%20characterized%20by%20repeated%20requests%20for%20delays%20in%20proceedings%2C%20has%20far-reaching%20implications%20for%20the%20efficiency%20and%20integrity%20of%20our%20legal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20addressing%20the%20All%20India%20District%20Judges%20Conference%20at%20Dhordo%20in%20Gujarat's%20Kutch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20adjournment%20and%20tareekh%20pe%20tareekh%20prolongs%20the%20agony%20of%20litigants.%20Common%20citizen%20feels%20that%20adjournment%20is%20part%20of%20judicial%20process%20and%20my%20experience%20is%20that%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20decide%20a%20complex%20case%20with%20a%20judgment%20than%20to%20persuade%20a%20lawyer%20to%20argue%20a%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20expressed%20concern%20that%20the%20longstanding%20principle%20of%20%26quot%3Bbail%20is%20the%20rule%2C%20jail%20is%20the%20exception%26quot%3B%20is%20losing%20ground%20with%20district%20courts%20hesitating%20to%20deal%20with%20matters%20involving%20personal%20liberty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImagine%20a%20victim%20of%20sexual%20assault%20whose%20case%20remains%20unresolved%20in%20the%20courts%20for%20several%20years.%20Isn't%20this%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20access%20justice%3F%20The%20concept%20of%20access%20to%20justice%20should%20extend%20beyond%20mere%20access%20to%20the%20courts%3B%20it%20should%20also%20guarantee%20that%20citizens%20receive%20timely%20judgments%20from%20courts%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20even%20one%20adjournment%20might%20look%20like%20a%20routine%20affair%2C%20it%20can%20have%20severe%20ramifications%20for%20the%20litigants%2C%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOften%2C%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20legal%20battle%20never%20comes%20to%20light%20during%20the%20farmer's%20lifetime.%20Instead%2C%20the%20burden%20falls%20upon%20their%20legal%20heirs%2C%20who%20find%20themselves%20embroiled%20in%20protracted%20legal%20proceedings%20long%20after%20their%20loved%20one's%20passing.%20We%20should%20not%20wait%20for%20our%20citizens%20to%20die%20for%20their%20case%20to%20be%20decided%20by%20a%20court%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourts%20nationwide%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20noted%2C%20are%20grappling%20with%20a%20significant%20backlog%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Balarming%20level%20of%20pending%20cases%26quot%3B.%20This%20backlog%20and%20pendency%20of%20cases%20present%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20efficient%20administration%20of%20justice%20and%20the%20timely%20resolution%20of%20legal%20disputes%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAddressing%20the%20backlog%20and%20pendency%20of%20cases%20requires%20a%20multi-faceted%20approach%20encompassing%20systemic%20reforms%2C%20procedural%20enhancements%2C%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20technological%20solutions.%20Efforts%20to%20streamline%20court%20procedures%2C%20expedite%20case%20disposal%2C%20and%20promote%20alternative%20dispute%20resolution%20mechanisms%20can%20help%20alleviate%20the%20burden%20on%20the%20judicial%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20can%20be%20a%20great%20tool%20for%20improving%20efficiency%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20sunshine%20is%20said%20to%20be%20the%20best%20disinfectant%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20technology%20is%20the%20best%20tool%20at%20our%20disposal%20to%20eliminate%20the%20inefficiency%20and%20opacity%20surrounding%20judicial%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20inclusivity%20and%20diversity%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20much%20improvement%20has%20been%20made%20towards%20achieving%20greater%20gender%20representation%20with%20women%20now%20constituting%2036.3%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20working%20strength%20of%20the%20district%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20while%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20in%20terms%20of%20gender%20representation%2C%20there%20remains%20a%20pressing%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20judicial%20institutions%20are%20truly%20inclusive%20and%20accommodating%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudges%20should%20not%20be%20unduly%20affected%20by%20criticism%20and%20commentary%20on%20social%20media%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20times%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20noticeable%20increase%20in%20judges%20facing%20criticisms%20and%20commentary%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%20And%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20I%20have%20had%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20scrutiny%20too!%20Even%20if%20I%20say%20just%20a%20single%20word%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20get%20reported%20faster%20than%20a%20speeding%20bullet.%20But%2C%20should%20we%2C%20judges%2C%20be%20unduly%20affected%20by%20this%3F%20The%20role%20of%20a%20judge%20is%20to%20dispense%20justice%20impartially%2C%20without%20being%20swayed%20by%20external%20pressures%20or%20public%20opinions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709399880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbo0hsb0o_chief-justice-1200_625x300_26_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-spotlights-adjournment-culture-in-judicial-system-5164549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20perception%20that%20adjournment%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20judicial%20system%20is%20disheartening%2C%20underlined%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Ch