ude%20to%20the%20guests%20and%20sharing%20heartfelt%20sentiments%20as%20the%20Ambani%20family%20prepares%20to%20welcome%20Anant's%20bride-to-be%20Radhika%20Merchant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fisha-ambanis-heartwarming-speech-at-anant-ambanis-pre-wedding-bash%2Farticleshow%2F108167069.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Police%20Submits%20Closure%20Report%20In%20Cheating%20Case%20Against%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Citing%20%26quot%3BMistake%20of%20Facts%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11103455%2FF5k08sFWsAAr9LD.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMumbai%3A%20After%20accusing%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20leader%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20of%20cheating%20and%20criminal%20breach%20of%20trust%20in%20the%20alleged%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20scam%20at%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Cooperative%20Bank%20(MSCB)%2C%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20of%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20now%20claimed%20that%20a%20criminal%20case%20was%20filed%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20mistake%20of%20facts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20March%201%2C%20the%20EOW%20filed%20a%20%E2%80%98C%20summary%E2%80%99%20report%20before%20the%20special%20court%20in%20Mumbai.%20A%20%E2%80%98C%20summary%E2%80%99%20report%20is%20filed%20when%20the%20investigating%20agency%20is%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20a%20person%20is%20wrongly%20implicated%20in%20a%20case%20due%20to%20mistake%20of%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20then%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20court%20before%20the%20case%20is%20closed%20against%20the%20person.%20The%20report%20was%20filed%20through%20special%20public%20prosecutor%20Raja%20Thackery.%20Special%20judge%20R.N.%20Rokade%20of%20Mumbai%20sessions%20court%20has%20adjourned%20the%20matter%20until%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20take%20the%20final%20call%20on%20whether%20to%20accept%20the%20closure%20report%20or%20to%20direct%20the%20police%20to%20conduct%20further%20investigation%20and%20subsequently%20file%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%E2%80%99s%20move%20is%20not%20surprising.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20pattern%20in%20both%20the%20state%20and%20central%20agencies%E2%80%99%20conduct%20in%20cases%20involving%20leaders%2C%20more%20specifically%20of%20those%20from%20the%20opposition%20who%20have%20jumped%20ships%20to%20join%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20or%20form%20an%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20EOW%20has%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20in%20the%20matter.%20In%202020%2C%20when%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tri-party%20government%20comprising%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%94%20was%20in%20power%2C%20the%20EOW%20had%20first%20filed%20a%20closure%20report.%20Pawar%20was%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20even%20then.%20The%20closure%20report%20was%20against%20Pawar%20and%2070%20others%20named%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20the%20MVA%20government%20collapsed%20in%20the%20state%20and%20BJP%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20took%20over%2C%20the%20EOW%20had%20suddenly%20shown%20interest%20in%20%E2%80%9Creinvestigating%E2%80%9D%20the%20matter.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20the%20EOW%20had%20said%20that%20it%20would%20want%20to%20further%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-2024-elections-near-ed-accelerates-actions-against-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3E%20As%202024%20Elections%20Near%2C%20ED%20Accelerates%20Actions%20Against%20Opposition%20Leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20months%2C%20Pawar%20had%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20became%20the%20second%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20July%202023%2C%20with%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20already%20holding%20that%20post.%20For%20this%2C%20Pawar%20had%20parted%20ways%20with%20his%20uncle%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20NCP%20party%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20several%20other%20MLAs%20left.%20Recently%2C%20the%20election%20commission%20granted%20him%20the%20party%20name%20and%20symbol%2C%20forcing%20Sharad%20Pawar%20to%20rename%20his%20party%20as%20NCP-Sharadchandra%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20published%20a%20detailed%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20suddenly%20all%20allegations%20against%20them%20were%20either%20dropped%20or%20the%20state%20machinery%20had%20lost%20interest%20in%20investigating%20the%20matter%20any%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%20alone%20some%20eight%20leaders%20have%20either%20left%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20or%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20or%20the%20Congress%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20fearing%20adverse%20action%20against%20them.%20Each%20of%20them%20are%20facing%20investigation%20either%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Department%20(ED)%20or%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAjit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20case%20history%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW%E2%80%99s%20case%20dates%20back%20to%202019%20when%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20had%20ordered%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20matter%20following%20a%20petition.%20The%20EOW%20filed%20the%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20in%20the%20case%20and%20all%20accused%20were%20booked%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20sections%20406%20(criminal%20breach%20of%20trust)%20and%20420%20(cheating)%2C%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%2C%20and%20Securitisation%20and%20Reconstruction%20of%20Financial%20Assets%20and%20Enforcement%20of%20Security%20Interest%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20loans%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20were%20obtained%20by%20sugar%20cooperatives%2C%20spinning%20mills%20and%20other%20entities%20from%20district%20and%20cooperative%20banks%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20allegedly%20had%20direct%20link%20as%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20directors%20of%20the%20MSC%20bank%20then.%20The%20loans%20were%20allegedly%20procured%20through%20illegal%20means%20and%20the%20EOW%20claimed%20to%20have%20found%20many%20irregularities%20in%20the%20procurement%20process.%20According%20to%20the%20EOW%E2%80%99s%20FIR%2C%20the%20state%20exchequer%20suffered%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20crore%20between%20January%201%2C%202007%2C%20and%20December%2031%2C%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20filed%20a%20separate%20offence%20alleging%20money-laundering%20based%20on%20the%20EOW%E2%80%99s%20case.%20It%20has%20so%20far%20filed%20two%20chargesheets%2C%20including%20against%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20faction%20MLA%20Prajakt%20Tanpure.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20base%20offence%2C%20like%20the%20EOW%20case%2C%20the%20ED%20cannot%20continue%20with%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709395229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11103455%2FF5k08sFWsAAr9LD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmumbai-police-scraps-cheating-case-against-ajit-pawar-citing-mistake-of-facts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20series%20of%20coincidences%2C%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20having%20central%20agencies%20chasing%20them%20and%20then%20when%20they%20defect%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20pursuit%20appears%20to%20stop.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22