ts%20later%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20long%20negotiations%2C%20in%20which%20UNRWA%20had%20agreed%20to%20EU%20conditions.%20The%20United%20Nations%20launched%20an%20internal%20investigation%20into%20the%20affair%2C%20and%20the%20EU%20is%20conducting%20an%20independent%20probe%20with%20its%20own%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exchange%20of%20correspondence%20with%20the%20EU%2C%20UNRWA%20Commissioner-General%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20assured%20the%20Commission%20that%20his%20organisation%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack%20in%20Israel%2C%20and%20that%20all%20of%20his%2013%2C000%20members%20of%20staff%20working%20in%20the%20besieged%20Gaza%20Strip%20were%20being%20reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20in%20a%20February%20meeting%20with%20EU%20foreign%20ministers%2C%20Lazzarini%20said%20that%20Israeli%20officials%20had%20yet%20to%20provide%20any%20evidence%20for%20the%20accusations%20leveled%20against%20the%20relief%20organisation.%20A%20UN%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20that%20they%20were%20still%20waiting%20for%20Israel%20to%20provide%20records%20or%20other%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20ongoing%20assault%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20in%20Gaza%2C%20EU%20foreign%20ministers%20recognised%20that%20UNRWA%20was%20essential%20to%20providing%20at%20least%20basic%20relief%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgaza-how-much-humanitarian-aid-is-getting-through%2Fa-67203929%5C%22%3Ebeleaguered%20population%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEU%20boosting%20humanitarian%20aid%20through%20partners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20has%20also%20announced%20it%20would%20pledge%20an%20additional%20%E2%82%AC68%20million%20in%20emergency%20support%20for%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20to%20be%20paid%20through%20international%20aid%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20International%20Federation%20of%20Red%20Cross%20and%20Red%20Crescent%20Societies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20funds%20will%20be%20provided%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20%E2%82%AC125%20million%20already%20allotted%20for%20this%20year.%20That%20would%20bring%20the%20total%20sum%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20for%20Palestinians%2C%20whether%20through%20UNRWA%20or%20through%20other%20international%20organizations%2C%20to%C2%A0%E2%82%AC275%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20increase%2C%20European%20Commission%20President%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20stand%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20Gaza%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20region.%20Innocent%20Palestinians%20should%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20the%20crimes%20of%20terrorist%20group%20Hamas.%20They%20face%20terrible%20conditions%20putting%20their%20lives%20at%20risk%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20sufficient%20food%20and%20other%20basic%20needs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDeeply%20disturbed%20by%20images%20from%20Gaza.%20Every%20effort%20must%20be%20made%20to%20investigate%20what%20happened%20and%20ensure%20transparency%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHumanitarian%20aid%20is%20a%20lifeline%20for%20those%20in%20need%20and%20access%20to%20it%20must%20be%20ensured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20stand%20by%20civilians%2C%20urging%20their%20protection%20in%20line%20with%20international%20law%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20(%40vonderleyen)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvonderleyen%2Fstatus%2F1763504038262251792%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EU%20is%20the%20third-largest%20donor%20to%20UNRWA%20after%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Funited-states-of-america%2Ft-19065189%5C%22%3EUS%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20Germany.%20In%20January%2C%2