C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fahead-of-polls-fci-to-spend-15-crore-in-five-states-for-delivering-foodgrains-in-bags-with-pm-modis-photo%2Farticle67904320.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20RTI%20replies%20received%20by%20activist%20Ajay%20Bose%2C%20the%20regional%20offices%20of%20the%20Food%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(FCI)%20have%20finalised%20tenders%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Tripura%2C%20and%20Meghalaya%20for%20procuring%20%E2%80%9Cwoven%20laminated%20bags%20with%20an%20indicative%20logo%20of%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%9D%20to%20distribute%20food%20grains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20RTI%20reply%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20West%20Bengal%20region%2C%20selection%20of%20company%20for%20production%20of%20bags%20is%20under%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Rajasthan%20FCI%20office%20is%20spending%20Rs%2013.29%20crore%20for%201.07%20crore%20synthetic%20bags%2C%20for%20Tripura%2C%20Rs%2085.51%20lakh%20is%20being%20spent%20on%205.98%20lakh%20Modi-branded%20bags.%20The%20Meghalaya%20regional%20office%20is%20spending%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%2052.75%20lakh%20for%204.22%20lakh%20bags%20and%20for%20Mizoram%2C%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20is%20being%20spent%20for%20procuring%201.75-lakh%20such%20bags%2C%20as%20per%20the%20RTI%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sikkim%2C%20the%20process%20is%20pending%20as%20bags%20are%20still%20being%20produced%20while%20a%20private%20company%20has%20been%20selected%20for%20the%20supply.%20The%20FCI%20is%20looking%20to%20procure%2098%2C000%20bags%20at%20Rs%2014.65%20apiece%2C%20totalling%20Rs%2014.35%20lakh%20in%20this%20eastern%20state%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20added%2C%20as%20per%20the%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20per%20piece%20procurement%20cost%20of%20the%20bags%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20logo%20is%20slightly%20different%20in%20each%20state.%20While%20each%20bag%20in%20Sikkim%20is%20being%20bought%20by%20the%20FCI%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2014.65%2C%20in%20Mizoram%20and%20Tripura%20it%20is%20at%20Rs%2014.30%20apiece%2C%20Rs%2012.5%20per%20per%20bag%20in%20Meghalaya%20and%20Rs%2012.375%20per%20bag%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpre-election-pm-modi-logos-on-pds-grain-bags-to-cost-crores-report%5C%22%3EPre-Election%20%E2%80%98PM%20Modi%20Logos%E2%80%99%20on%20PDS%20Grain%20Bags%20to%20Cost%20Crores%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20an%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fahead-of-election-fci-starts-process-to-procure-bags-with-photos-of-pm-modi-for-foodgrain-distribution%2Farticle67853977.ece%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20FCI%20had%20directed%20all%20of%20its%2026%20regional%20offices%20to%20float%20tenders%20for%20procuring%20woven%20laminated%20bags%20with%C2%A0%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20logo%20for%20distribution%20of%20food%20grains%20under%20the%20PMGKAY%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20free%20grain%20distribution%20under%20PMGKAY%20that%20started%20in%202020%20when%20the%20pandemic%20began%2C%20unbranded%2050%20kg%20jute%20sacks%20were%20used%20to%20disburse%20grain.%20The%20branding%20of%20bags%20with%20faces%20of%20political%20figures%20has%20begun%20in%202024%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709371853000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F17115300%2F7637937542_b870fe2c5e_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-lok-sabha-polls-fci-to-spend-rs-15-crore-to-buy-foodgrain