ool%20till%20class%20V%20in%20our%20village.%20For%20higher%20studies%2C%20we%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20go%20out.%20This%20was%20the%20period%20when%20most%20of%20the%20girls%20would%20drop%20out.%20Anyway%2C%20I%20pushed%20myself%20to%20study%20till%20class%2012%20at%20least%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20this%2C%20I%20would%20walk%20for%20three%20kilometres%20to%20the%20highway%20to%20catch%20a%20bus%20to%20the%20school%20that%20was%20further%20eight%20km%20away.%20In%20all%2C%20I%20would%20daily%20travel%2011%20km%20to%20reach%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20additional%20woes%20of%20the%20village%2C%20she%20informs%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20proper%20drainage%20system%20in%20the%20village.%20Often%2C%20drains%20would%20overflow%20on%20the%20pathways%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20move%20about.%20This%20would%20also%20become%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20mosquitoes.%20Doctors%20did%20not%20stay%20long%20in%20our%20village%20because%20of%20poor%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20huge%20patient%20workload.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-3-1709127524.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20model%20village%20has%20become%20energy%20self-sufficient%20and%20has%20provided%20tap%20water%20connections%20to%20the%20rural%20households.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-3-1709127524.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-3-1709127524-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Ftelangana-village-3-1709127524-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20h