nt-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20dogs%20find%20peace%2C%20quiet%20and%20support%20at%20this%20shelter.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDogs%20who%20had%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20live%20when%20they%20first%20came%20to%20our%20shelter%20end%20up%20living%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20number%20of%20dogs%20under%20our%20care%20has%20increased.%20Also%2C%20no%20one%20comes%20back%20to%20adopt%20paraplegic%20dogs%20because%20they%20poop%20and%20pee%20wherever%20they%20can%20drag%20themselves.%20People%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20patience%20to%20adopt%20them%20once%20they%E2%80%99re%20rescued%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaaman%20also%20houses%20a%20few%20abandoned%20breeds.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20will%20come%20and%20tie%20their%20Rottweilers%2C%20Labradors%2C%20Great%20Danes%20and%20German%20Shepherds%20to%20the%20gate%20and%20go%20away.%20People%20sometimes%20leave%20a%20cardboard%20box%20with%20five%20newborn%20indie%20puppies%20taken%20away%20from%20their%20mother%20at%20our%20gate%20as%20well.%20Who%20adopts%20them%3F%20Where%20do%20I%20find%20homes%20for%20these%20breeds%3F%20We%E2%80%99ve%20not%20had%20very%20good%20luck%20with%20breeds%20we%20have%20given%20out%20for%20adoption.%20I%20will%20not%20give%20a%20dog%20for%20adoption%20until%20and%20unless%20I%20know%20the%20person%20or%20someone%20recommends%20the%20%E2%80%98dog-parents%E2%80%99%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Sarah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20we%20recently%20had%20one%20Dalmatian%20puppy%20%E2%80%98Simi%E2%80%99%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20hole%20in%20her%20heart%20and%20doctors%20said%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20survive%20this%20condition.%20Thankfully%2C%20she%20has%20been%20with%20us%20for%20about%20eight%20to%20nine%20months%20now.%20Forget%20about%20paying%20us%20for%20her%20upkeep%2C%20the%20people%20who%20dropped%20her%20here%20haven%E2%80%99t%20even%20called%20to%20check%20up%2